ggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jjh1665703211229.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jjh1665703211229.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jjh1665703211229.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jjh1665703211229\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Logicals for the Uniface Web Application Server are set in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span> assignment file. They are used to control error pages and output filters.\n </p>\n<p class=\"lines\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">; wasv.asn</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">[LOGICALS]</code><br/><var class=\"keyword varname\">Logical = Value</var><br/>      </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Web Application Server Logicals</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Logical</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">More Information</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYSHTTPTITLE</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the web error page title</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"5\">\n<p class=\"p\">The USYSHTTP component uses these logicals in default error reporting.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"egv1665702669743.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/egv1665702669743.html\" title=\"An error is displayed when a problem occurs in executing the desired Uniface service, for example, if an incorrect URL is provided.\">Web Application Error Pages</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYSHTTPHEADER</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the heading on the web error page</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYSHTTPBODY</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the web error page text</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYSHTTPBGCOLOR</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the web error page background color</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYSHTTPBACKGROUND</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set the web error background image</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lab1665703211298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lab1665703211298.html\" title=\"Specifies a comma-separated list of plug-in components that can add JavaScript to web pages generated by DSPs and USPs.\">UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">List the plug-in components for adding JavaScript to web pages generated by DSPs and USPs</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jjh1665703211229__table_d16367e1_d16368e1_d16369e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"urh1665702755394.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/urh1665702755394.html\" title=\"Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages.\">Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528907\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528907\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Web Application Server Logicals Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Logicals for the Uniface Web Application Server are set in the wasv.asn assignment file. They are used to control error pages and output filters. ; wasv.asn [LOGICALS] Logical = Value Table 1. Web Application Server Logicals Logical Description More Information USYSHTTPTITLE Set the web error page title The USYSHTTP component uses these logicals in default error reporting. For more information, see Web Application Error Pages USYSHTTPHEADER Set the heading on the web error page USYSHTTPBODY Set the web error page text USYSHTTPBGCOLOR Set the web error page background color USYSHTTPBACKGROUND Set the web error background image UWEBOUTPUTFILTERS List the plug-in components for adding JavaScript to web pages generated by DSPs and USPs Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}